  "title": "Christmas Containers",
  "description": "A simple resource pack that makes chests have the Christmas skin all year plus custom barrels and shulkers.",
  "body": "# Christmas Containers!\n\nI wish you a merry **Craftmas**.\n\nWelcome to the resource pack that compliments all your needs if you're looking for a good **Christmas** pack. I didn't add much to the pack, but as the name suggests, it has **Christmas** themed containers.\n\n### The containers:\n- Christmas chests all year!\n> - both normal and trapped\n- Christmas enderchest\n- Barrels with wreath on the opening on it\n- Shulkers have gotten wrapped to look like presents\n\n![All the containers](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5d2c2735c3b96cd5f47127110f9fba8c8ae83aba_0.webp)\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pnPewT4xpE\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/347e3d1419da95e567713c06878aa2dab4b14c30.png\" alt=\"Join the Discord server\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n\n## Other projects:\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/armored-vanguard\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c9ed2b7145c975776d07353bd57247825ad1b852_0.webp\" alt=\"Armored Vanguard\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/armored-vanguard-dyed-knights\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/86ed16bfaa663826eb949e88736a5bf32daf1532_0.webp\" alt=\"Armored Vanguard: Dyed Knights\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/spears-to-lances\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e223d249862cd3bf02859137f046ca13427af596.png\" alt=\"Spears to Lances\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/short-weaponry\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6cf1924ce42cb95f5cbb303395cca699ec6c2301.png\" alt=\"Short Weaponry\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/nomex-helmets\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8316fb689873e46e8bb67397d82f295730ee6afc.png\" alt=\"Racing Helmets\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\"></a>",
